Class AbstractConceptExtensionProvider<T extends IConceptExtension>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.mrcm.core.extensions.AbstractConceptExtensionProvider<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The collected extension type
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ExtensionBasedConceptModelExtensionProvider, ExtensionBasedConceptPropagatorProvider, ExtensionBasedConceptValidatorProvider

    public abstract class AbstractConceptExtensionProvider<T extends IConceptExtension>
extends Object
    Represents an abstract extension provider that collects extension keyed by their "id" attributes and collects applicable extensions for Concepts.
